<sect1 id="styles">
<title
>Iintlobo</title>

<para
>Xa usakha amaxwebhu anzima kuneleta yeshishini, njenge ncwadi, ileta yendaba, okanye qala kwakhona, uxwebhu lwaphulwa rhoqo kumacandelo. Icandelo ngalinye kula linokuba nenkangeleko efanayo. </para>

<para
>Ungasebenzisa iitlobo ukugcina lula ujongo oluqinileyo ngapha kolwakho uxwebhu.</para>

<tip
> <para
>Ukuba uqhelene ne <quote
>Iintlobo</quote
> kwi &Microsoft; <application
>Igama</application
>, &kword; iintlobo zenza imisebenzi eminye. Ungatsibela kwicandelo elilandelayo.</para
> </tip>

<para
>Njengomzekelo, ukuba sijonga kuxwebhu olusikiweyo, kwaye senze iintlobo ezahlukeneyo kumaqela angawo :</para>

