<para
>Kulo mzekelo, ungabona le ncwadi yecomputer ukuba iqulathe amacandelo amabini. Kwiwonga lokubhaliweyo lecandelo ngalinye, sitshintshe uhlobo lokubhaliweyo kwi <quote
>Iwonga Lecandelo</quote
>. Okuseleyo koxwebhu kushiywe njenge <quote
>Okubhaliweyo Okuqhelekileyo</quote
>.</para>

<para
>Asifuni ukwazi indlela esifuna ngayo okubhaliweyo nemihlathi yala macandelo ajongeke ngayo. Konke esifuna ukukwenza kukuqwalasela la macandelo okubhaliweyo njenge <quote
>Amawonga Ecandelo</quote
> okanye <quote
>Okubhaliweyo Okuqhelekileyo</quote
></para>

<para
>Xa silugqibile uxwebhu, ungatshintsha ujongeko lwako konke okubhaliweyo okunombhalo <quote
>Iwonga Lecandelo</quote
> zonke kunye. </para>

<para
>Oku kuzakuqinisekisa ukuba onke amawonga ecandelo avela eqinile ngapha koxwebhu lakho.</para>

<para
>&kword; ineNtlobo eziyi 11 ezichaziweyo. Kuluhlu lwazo, nee nketho zofomato, <link linkend="predefined-styles"
>nqakraza apha</link
>.</para>

<sect2 id="style-select">
<title
>Itshintsha Uhlobo lokubhaliweyo</title>

<para
>Ukutshintsha uhlobo lokubhaliweyo, kuqala, <link linkend="select"
>khetha okubhaliweyo</link
> ofuna utshintsho lufakwe kulo.</para>

<para
>Ungatshintsha ngoku uhlobo lomsebenzi kwenye yendlela ezimbini:</para>

<itemizedlist
> <listitem
> <para
>Khetha <menuchoice
> <guimenu
>Fomati</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Uhlobo</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> kwiMenu bar. Oku kuzakuvula uluhlu lweentlobo ezikhoyo, khetha uhlobo kuluhlu.</para
> </listitem
> <listitem
> <para
>Ungakhetha uhlobo usebenzisa ibhokisi yolahlo phantsi kwibar-Yesixhobo Yomsebenzi Wofomato. ( <inlinemediaobject
><imageobject
><imagedata fileref="chstylebut.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
></inlinemediaobject
> )</para
> </listitem
> </itemizedlist>

</sect2>

<sect2 id="style-add">
<title
>Yenza Uhlobo</title>

<para
>Ukuba uceba ukusebenzisdda Iintlobo kuxwebhu olukhulu, uzakufuina ukwenza iintlobo ezintsha zeemfuno zakho. </para>

<para
>Ukwenza uhlobo olutsha:</para>

<procedure
> <step
> <para
>Khetha <menuchoice
> <guimenu
>Ngaphezulu</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Umlungisi</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> kwiMenu bar.</para
><para
>Oku kuzakuzisa ibhokisi yencoko yababini</para
> <screenshot
> <mediaobject
> <imageobject
> <imagedata fileref="styldlg1.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
> </mediaobject
> </screenshot
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Nqakraza <guibutton
>Dibanisa</guibutton
>.</para
> <para
>Oku kuzakuzisa enye ibhokisi yencoko yababini</para
> <screenshot
> <mediaobject
> <imageobject
><imagedata fileref="styldlg3.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
> </mediaobject
> </screenshot
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Chwetheza igama elichazayo kwibhokisi enombhalo <guilabel
>Igama</guilabel
>. Eli izakuba ligama lohlobo.</para
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Ngoku khetha uhlobo kwibhokisi yolahlo-phantsi enombhalo <guilabel
>Ilandela Uhlobo le Template</guilabel
>. Oku kuzakuba ngundoqo wohlobo omguqula kancinane ukwenza uhlobo lwakho olutsha (Kufuneka uqale naphi na ekunene?). Ukuba uyathandabuza, <quote
>Esezantsi</quote
> ilungile.</para
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Ngoku ungenza utshintsho ofuna ukwenza uhlobo olutsha lwakho ngalo.</para
> <para
>Ibhokisi yemboniso izakubonisa indlela uhlobo lwakho olutsha luzakujongeka ngayo.</para
> <para
>Sebenzisa amaqhosha anombhalo <link linkend="style-font"
>Umgca</link
>, <link linkend="style-color"
>Umbala</link
>, <link linkend="style-space"
>Isithuba na Mathanda</link
>, <link linkend="style-align"
>Ukwenza umgca</link
>, <link linkend="style-borders"
>Imida</link
>, <link linkend="style-numbering"
>Amanani</link
>, ne <link linkend="style-tabulators"
>Izilungisi-sithuba</link
> ukwenza uhlobo.</para
> <para
>Ukuba ufuna ukutshintsha ithambeka lohlobo, bona icandelo eliwongwe <link linkend="style-controlling"
>Ilawula Iintlobo</link
>.</para
> <para
>Nqakraza <guibutton
>KULUNGILE</guibutton
> ukwenza uhlobo lwakho olutsha.</para
> <para
>Nqakraza <guibutton
>Cima</guibutton
> ukulahla ukwenziwa kohlobo.</para
> </step
> </procedure>

<sect3 id="style-font">
<title
>Itshintsha Ubungakanani bomgca, Udidi njalo-njalo.</title>

<para
>Ungatshintsha ubungakanani bomgca, iqela lomsebenzi, umgca, iqela lomsebenzi kwaye qhobosha okukekeleyo nobuso obukhulu ngokunqakraza kwi <guilabel
>Umgca</guilabel
>. Oku kuzakuvula ibhokisi yencoko yababini entsha.</para>

<screenshot>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="fchardlg.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para
>Usebenzisa le bhokisi yencoko yababini, ungakhetha umgca, ubungakanani, iqela lomsebenzi, kekeleyo neenketho zobuso obukhulu.</para>

<para
>Ibhokisi yemboniso ngezantsi, izakubonisa indlela izicwangciso zakho zangoku zizakuvela ngayo</para>

<para
>Inqakraza <guibutton
>KULUNGILE</guibutton
> izakubophelela utshintsho lwakho kuhlobo.</para>

<para
>Inqakraza <guibutton
>Cima</guibutton
> izakulahla lonke utshintsho olwenziweyo kule bhokisi yencoko yababini.</para>

</sect3>

<sect3 id="style-color">
<title
>Itshintsha umbala womgca</title>

<para
>Ungatshintsha umbala womgca wohlobo lakho olutsha, ngokunqakraza kwi <guilabel
>Umbala</guilabel
>.</para>

<para
>Ungakhetha ngoku umbala wokubhaliweyo okukhethiweyo usebenzisa i <link linkend="select-colors"
>Ibhokisi Yencoko yababini Yokhetho Lombala</link
>.</para>

</sect3>

<sect3 id="style-space">
<title
>Itshintsha Isithuba Somhlathi na Mathanda</title>

<para
>Ukutshintsha isithuba somhlathi namathanda omhlathi wohlobo lakho, nqakraza kwi "Isithuba na Mathanda". Oku kuvula ibhokisi entsha yencoko yababini.</para>

<screenshot>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="styldlg4.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para
>Le bhokisi yencoko yababini ikuvumela ucwangcise imida yomhlathi, isithuba phakathi kweelayini, nesithuba phakathi kwemihlathi.</para>

<para
>Icandelo lokuqala lale bhokisi yencoko yababini inombhalo <guilabel
>Ithanda</guilabel
>, kwaye iqulathe amaqela amathathu:</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Ekhohlo</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ungazenza amathanda zonke iilayini zomhlathi ngokungenisa ixabiso kule bhokisi. Ilayini yokuqala ayichatshazelwa yile bhokisi. Ukuba ufuna ukulungisa ilayini yokuqala, kufuneka ukhankanye oko ngokwahlukeneyo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Ekunene</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>!!!!Yenziwe mnyama nje!!!!!</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Ilayini Yokuqala</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Naliphi elingengo-nothi ixabiso elingeniswe kule bhokisi yokubhaliweyo, lizakubhekelisa umda osekhohlo welayini yokuqala.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<para
>Icandelo elilandelayo linombhalo <guilabel
>Isithuba Selayini</guilabel
>. I qulathe iziqalelo ezimbini.</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Ibhokisi yolahlo-phantsi</term
> <listitem
> <para
>!!!!!!!!!!!!!!Yenziwe mnyama!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Ibhokisi yokubhaliweyo</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ngokungenisa ixabiso apha, unganyenyisa isithubaphakathi kweelayini kokungagqibekanga. Ukuba ungenisa inani elililo, uza kunyusa isithubaphakathi kweelayini. Ukuba, kwesinye isandla, ungenisa inani elikhabanayo, uzakunciphisa isithuba phakathi kweelayini.</para
> <note
> <para
>Utshintsho kolu ngeno AZI chaphazeli isithuba selayini phakathi kweelayini zemihlathi eyahlukeneyo.</para
> </note
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<para
>Icandelo lokugqibela linombhalo <guilabel
>Isithuba Somhlathi</guilabel
> . iqulathe amangeno amabini:</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Phambi</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ngokungenisa ixabiso apha,  unganyenyisa isithuba phambi komhlathi ngamnye kwisithuba esingagqibekanga. Ukuba ungenisa inani elililo, uzakunyusa isithuba phambi komhlathi. Ukuba, kwesinye isandla, ungenisa inani elikhabayo, uzakunciphisa isithuba phambi komhlathi ngamnye.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Emva</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ngokungenisa ixabiso apha, unganyenyisa isithuba emva komhlathi ngamnye kwisithuba esingagqibekanga. Ukuba ungenisa inanin elililo, uzakunyusa isithuba emv akomhlathi. Ukuba, kwesinye isandla, ungenisa inani elikhabayo, uzakunciphisa isithuba emva komhlathi ngamnye.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<para
>Ekunene kwibhokisi yencoko yababini, yibhokisi yemboniso, ezaku <emphasis
>sondele</emphasis
> ubeko lokugqibela loxwebhu lakho.</para>

</sect3>

<sect3 id="style-align">
<title
>Itshintsha ukwenziwa komgca womhlathi</title>

<para
>Ukutshintsha indlela okubhaliweyo kubekwa ngayo kwilayini, nqakraza kwi <guilabel
>Ukwenza umgca</guilabel
>. Oku kuzakuvula ibhokisi yencoko yababini entsha.</para>

<screenshot>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject>
<imagedata fileref="styldlg5.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para
>Njengoko ubona, kukho iinketho ezine.</para>

<para
>Ukuba ukhetha <guilabel
>Ekhohlo</guilabel
>, <guilabel
>Ekunene</guilabel
> okanye <guilabel
>Umbindi</guilabel
>, okubhaliweyo kuzakususwa elayinini.</para>

<para
>Ukuba ukhetha <guilabel
>Ibloko</guilabel
>, &kword; izakunyusa isithuba <emphasis
>phakathi</emphasis
> amagama, ukuze ilayini nganye (ngaphandle kwelayini yokugqibela), ifikelela yomibini eyasekhohlo nasekunene imida.</para>

<para
>Ekunene kwibhokisi yencoko yababini, yibhokisi yemboniso, ezaku <emphasis
>sondele</emphasis
> ubeko lokugqibela loxwebhu lakho.</para>

</sect3>

<sect3 id="style-borders">
<title
>Itshintsha Imida Yomhlathi</title>

<para
>Ukudibanisa imida yohlobo lwakho, nqakraza kwi <guilabel
>Imida</guilabel
>. Oku kuzakuvula ibhokisi yencoko yababini entsha.</para>

<screenshot>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject
><imagedata fileref="styldlg6.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para
>Ungaxelela &kword; ijikeleze (kwamanye okanye onke amacala) umhlathi onomda. Lo mda unokuqina okanye hayi, nakowuphi umbala na kobuphi ubungakanani. Usebenzisa eli qela lencoko yababini ukunyenyisa imida.</para>

<para
>Ukuchaza imida yomhlathi, uqala ugqibe indlela imida ezakuvela ngayo kuxwebhu. Ngoku ukhetha ukuba yeyiphi imida yomhlathi ezakusetyenziswa. Ungaxuba kwaye uthelekise iintlobo, ubunzima nemibala yemida yomhlathi kugobeko olukhulu kuxwebhu lakho.</para>

