<sect2 id="style-edit">
<title
>Ihlela Uhlobo</title>

<para
>Amandla ayinyaniso entlobo, kukwenza uhlelo lweenketho ezifomatayo zolo hlobo <emphasis
>emva</emphasis
> uchaze uhlobo. Ngokutshintsha ufomato lohlobo, utshintsha ngokukhawuleza umhalthi ngamnye ngolo hlobo, kwaye ulondoloza ujongo oluqinileyo kuxwebhu lakho.</para>

<para
>Uzakuqwalasela kwakhona, ukuba ukuhlela iinketho zokufomata zohlobo, kusebenzisa ujongano olunye olusebenzise ukwenza uhlobo kwi ndawo yokuqala.</para>

<para
>Ukuhlela uhlobo lwangoku:</para>

<procedure
> <step
> <para
>Khetha <menuchoice
> <guimenu
>Ngaphezulu</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Umlungisi</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> kwiMenu bar.</para
><para
>Oku kuzakuzisa ibhokisi yencoko yababini</para
> <screenshot
> <mediaobject
> <imageobject
><imagedata fileref="styldlg1.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
> </mediaobject
> </screenshot
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Khetha uhlobo ofuna ukuluhlela kuluhlu ekhohlo</para
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Nqakraza <guibutton
