>.</para
> <para
>Oku kuzakuzisa enye ibhokisi yencoko yababini</para
> <screenshot
> <mediaobject
> <imageobject
><imagedata fileref="styldlg3.png" format="PNG"/> </imageobject
> </mediaobject
> </screenshot
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Ngoku ungenza utshintsho olufunayo kolu hlobo.</para
> <para
>Ibhokisi yemboniso izakubonisa indlela uhlobo lwakho olutsha luzakujongeka ngayo.</para
> <warning
> <para
>Sukutshintsha igama le template yakho.</para
> <para
>Ukwenza oko kuzakucima uhlobo lwangoku kuluhlu (kwaye yenza entsha ngegama elitsha).</para
> <para
>Nayiphi na imihlathi efomatwe ngoqobo ngolu hlobo, iza kubuyiselwa kwi <quote
>Esezantsi</quote
>.</para
> </warning
> <para
