<sect3 id="change-style-font">
<title
>Itshintsha Ubungakanani Bomgca, Udidi &etc;</title>

<para
>Ungatshintsha ubungakanani bomgca, iqela lomsebenzi, umgca, iqela lomsebenzi kwaye qhobosha okukekeleyo nobuso obukhulu ngokunqakraza kwi <guilabel
>Umgca</guilabel
>. Oku kuzakuvula ibhokisi yencoko yababini entsha.</para>

<screenshot>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject
><imagedata fileref="fchardlg.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para
>Usebenzisa le bhokisi yencoko yababini, ungakhetha umgca, ubungakanani, iqela lomsebenzi, kekeleyo neenketho zobuso obukhulu.</para>

<para
>Ibhokisi yemboniso ngezantsi, izakubonisa indlela izicwangciso zakho zangoku zizakuvela ngayo</para>

<para
>Inqakraza <guibutton
>KULUNGILE</guibutton
> izakubophelela utshintsho lwakho kuhlobo.</para>

<para
>Inqakraza <guibutton
>Cima</guibutton
> izakulahla lonke utshintsho olwenziweyo kule bhokisi yencoko yababini.</para>

</sect3>

<sect3 id="change-style-color">
<title
>Itshintsha umbala womgca</title>

<para
>Ungatshintsha umbala womgca wohlobo lwakho, ngokunqakraza kwi <guilabel
>Umbala</guilabel
>.</para>

<para
>Ungakhetha ngoku umbala wohlobo usebenzisa i <link linkend="select-colors"
>Ibhokisi Yencoko yababini Yokhetho Lombala</link
>.</para>

</sect3>

<sect3 id="change-style-spacing">
<title
>Itshintsha Isithuba Somhlathi na Mathanda</title>

<para
>Ukutshintsha isithuba somhlathi namathanda omhlathi wohlobo lwakho, nqakraza kwi <guilabel
>Isithuba na Mathanda</guilabel
>. Oku kuvula ibhokisi yencoko yababini entsha.</para>

<screenshot>
<mediaobject>
<imageobject
><imagedata fileref="styldlg4.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject>
</mediaobject>
</screenshot>

<para
>Le bhokisi yencoko yababini ikuvumela ucwangcise imida yomhlathi, isithuba phakathi kweelayini, nesithuba phakathi kwemihlathi.</para>

<para
>Icandelo lokuqala lale bhokisi yencoko yababini inombhalo <guilabel
>Ithanda</guilabel
>, kwaye iqulathe amaqela amathathu:</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Ekhohlo</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ungazenza amathanda zonke iilayini zomhlathi ngokungenisa ixabiso kule bhokisi. Ilayini yokuqala ayichatshazelwa yile bhokisi. Ukuba ufuna ukulungisa ilayini yokuqala, kufuneka ukhankanye oko ngokwahlukeneyo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Ekunene</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>!!!!Yenziwe mnyama nje!!!!!</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Ilayini Yokuqala</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Naliphi elingengo-nothi ixabiso elingeniswe kule bhokisi yokubhaliweyo, lizakubhekelisa umda osekhohlo welayini yokuqala.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<para
>Icandelo elilandelayo linombhalo <guilabel
>Isithuba Selayini</guilabel
>. I qulathe iziqalelo ezimbini.</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Ibhokisi yolahlo-phantsi</term
> <listitem
> <para
>!!!!!!!!!!!!!!Yenziwe mnyama!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
>Ibhokisi yokubhaliweyo</term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ngokungenisa ixabiso apha, unganyenyisa isithubaphakathi kweelayini kokungagqibekanga. Ukuba ungenisa inani elililo, uza kunyusa isithubaphakathi kweelayini. Ukuba, kwesinye isandla, ungenisa inani elikhabanayo, uzakunciphisa isithuba phakathi kweelayini.</para
> <note
> <para
>Utshintsho kolu ngeno lwenza <emphasis
>HAYI</emphasis
> ichaphazela isithuba selayini phakathi kweelayini zemihlathi eyahlukeneyo.</para
> </note
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<para
>Icandelo lokugqibela linombhalo <guilabel
>Isithuba Somhlathi</guilabel
>. I qulathe amangeno amabini:</para>

<variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Phambi</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ngokungenisa ixabiso apha,  unganyenyisa isithuba phambi komhlathi ngamnye kwisithuba esingagqibekanga. Ukuba ungenisa inani elililo, uzakunyusa isithuba phambi komhlathi. Ukuba, kwesinye isandla, ungenisa inani elikhabayo, uzakunciphisa isithuba phambi komhlathi ngamnye.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Emva</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ngokungenisa ixabiso apha, unganyenyisa isithuba emva komhlathi ngamnye kwisithuba esingagqibekanga. Ukuba ungenisa inanin elililo, uzakunyusa isithuba emv akomhlathi. Ukuba, kwesinye isandla, ungenisa inani elikhabayo, uzakunciphisa isithuba emva komhlathi ngamnye.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist>

<para
>Ekunene kwibhokisi yencoko yababini, yibhokisi yemboniso, ezaku <emphasis
>sondele</emphasis
> ubeko lokugqibela loxwebhu lakho.</para>

<para
>Nqakraza <guibutton
>KULUNGILE</guibutton
> ukwamkela utshintsho lwakho.</para>

<para
>Nqakraza <guibutton
>Cima</guibutton
> ukulahla naluphi na utshintsho olwenzileyo ngale bhokisi yencoko yababini.</para>

</sect3>

<sect3 id="change-style-align">
<title
