<sect2 id="style-controlling">
<title
>Ilawula iintlobo</title>

<para
>Ngamanye amaxwebhu, uzakufuna ukuqiniseka ukuba umsebenzi wonke kuxwebhu lakho <emphasis
>ngqo</emphasis
> ithelekiseka nohlobo loxwebhu. Ngamanye amaxwebhu, uzakufuna ugobeko olongeziweyo. Kulo mzekelo wesibvini, ufuna ukuqwalasela &kword; ngoko itshintsha kuphela iindlela ezithile into ezibonaklisa ngayo yohlobo ngoqgibo ngalunye.</para>

<para
>Ukuhlela uhlobo lwangoku:</para>

<procedure
> <step
> <para
>Khetha <menuchoice
> <guimenu
>Ngaphezulu</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>Umlungisi</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
> kwiMenu bar.</para
><para
>Oku kuzakuzisa ibhokisi yencoko yababini</para
> <screenshot
> <mediaobject
> <imageobject
><imagedata fileref="styldlg1.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
> </mediaobject
> </screenshot
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Ngoku nqakraza kwisithuba esinombhalo <guilabel
>Gqiba Uqwalaselo</guilabel
>.</para
> <screenshot
> <mediaobject
> <imageobject
> <imagedata fileref="styldlg2.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject
> </mediaobject
> </screenshot
> </step
> <step
> <para
>Le bhokisi yencoko yababini yaphulwe kumaqela ayi 7 angundoqo, neyodwa ibhokisi yokhangelo. </para
> <substeps
> <step
> <title
><guilabel
>Imigca</guilabel
></title
> <para
>Ibhokisi yolahlo yokuqala, igqiba ukuba zeziphi iziphumo zomgca uhlobo lunokuzilawula, kwaye naxa zizakufakwa. Iinketho zakho zale bhokisi yolahlo-phantsi zi:</para
> <variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Sukugqiba imigca</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ukuba olu khetho lukhethiwe, &kword; ayizukulungisa nayiphi imigca (nge ntlonipho kubungakanani, igama lomgca, kekeleyo okanye ubuso obukhulu, &etc;) xa ufaka uhlobo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Gqiba Iintsapho zomgca yemigca yonke enobungakanani</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Xa ikhethiwe, &kword; ayizukulungisa nawyiphi na imigca xa ufaka uhlobo ngaphandle kokuba isiphumo sobungakanani bemigca yokubhaliweyo okukhethiweyo siyathelekiseka nobungakanani bomgca kuhlobo. Ukuba ubungakanani bomgca abuthelekiseki, &kword; ayizukutshintsha naziphi na iziphumo zomgca. Ukuba ubungakanani abuthelekiseki, okubhaliweyo okukhethiweyo kuzakutshintshelwa kumgca wosapho lohlobo. Akukho olunye utshintsho (ubuso obukhulu, kekeleyo, &etc;) kuzakwenziwa.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Gqiba Iintsapho zomgca zemigca yonke enobungakanani</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ngolu khetho, &kword; izakuguqula Umgca Wosapho (kodwa akukho ezinye iziphumo), kumgca ochazwe kuhlobo ngaphandle kobungakanani bomgca.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Gqiba Iintsapho zomgca ne Ziphumo zemigca enobungakanani obunye</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Xa ikhethiwe, &kword; ayizukulungisa nayiphi imigca xa ifaka uhlobo ngaphandle kokuba isiphumo sobungakanani bemigca sokubhaliweyo okukhethiweyo siyathelekiseka nobungakanani bomgca kuhlobo. Ukuba ubungakanani bomgca ayithelekiseki, &kword; ayizukutshintsha naziphi iziphumo zomgca. Ukuba ubungakanani abuthelekiseki, okubhaliweyo okukhethiweyo kuzakutshintshwa ukuthelekisa uhlobo. Zonke iziphumo (ubuso obukhulu, ezikekeleyo, &etc;) zizakutshintshwa.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Gqiba Iintsapho zomgca ne Ziphumo zemigca yonke enobungakanani</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ngolu khetho, &kword; izakutshintsha konke okubhaliweyo, ngaphandle kobungakanani okanye iziphumo, ukuthelekisa umgca okhankanywe kuhlobo.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> </variablelist
> </step
> <step
> <title
><guilabel
>Umbala womgca</guilabel
></title
> <para
>Le bhokisi yolahlo phantsi ikuvumela ukhankanye ukuba imibala Yomgca izaku tshintshwa ukuthelekisa uhlobo okanye hayi.</para
> <variablelist
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Sukugqib aimibala</guilabel
></term
> <listitem
> <para
>Ukuba olu khetho lukhethiwe, &kword; ayizukulungisa nayiphi imibala yomgca.</para
> </listitem
> </varlistentry
> <varlistentry
> <term
><guilabel
>Gqiba imibala</guilabel
></term
